# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [2.0.1] - 2024-09-06

- update Contributing & README files style spacing
- add function to install npm dependencies
- remove duplicated message

## [2.0.0] - 2024-09-05

- **Major refactor** of the project structure:
  - Removed `awesome-lazy-zsh.js`.
  - Updated `package.json` to reflect the new structure.
  - Reduced dependencies to only `chalk` and `prompts`.
  - Updated README and contributing guidelines.

## [1.0.2] - 2024-08-16

- Added `repository`, `homepage`, `bugs`, and `bin` fields in `package.json`.
- Improved keywords and added a `start` script.
- Updated README with new instructions.

## [1.0.1] - 2024-08-15

- Added support for Starship and Spaceship themes.
- Improved error handling in the setup script.

## [1.0.0] - 2024-08-14

- Initial release with default and custom installation options.
